ğŸ“Œ Overview

Health Tracker is a Node.js + Express web application that allows users to:
Register and log in securely (bcrypt-hashed passwords)
Create, view, search, edit, and delete workout logs
Maintain personal workout history stored in a MySQL database
Use a clean, responsive interface with EJS templates
The application runs on the Goldsmiths DOC server via Node.js and MySQL.

ğŸš€ Features Implemented
âœ… User Authentication
Secure login & registration
Password hashing using bcrypt
Express sessions to maintain login state
Login required for all workout routes
âœ… Workout Management (CRUD)
Add a workout
List all workouts
Edit a workout
Delete a workout

Search workouts
Each workout includes:
Date
Type
Duration (minutes)
Intensity
Notes
âœ… Security Measures
Bcrypt password hashing
express-sanitizer for form input
Session-based access control
Parameterized MySQL queries (prevents SQL injection)
ğŸ—„ Database Structure
Database: health
Table: workouts
Field	Type	Description
id	INT PK AI	Workout ID
user_id	INT	Owner of the workout
workout_date	DATE	Date of workout
workout_type	VARCHAR	Activity type
duration_minutes	INT	Duration in minutes
intensity	VARCHAR	Low / Medium / High
notes	TEXT	Optional notes
Users Table: users
Field	Description
id	Primary key
first	First name
last	Last name
email	Email
username	Username
password	Bcrypt hashed pass
